The following classes have already completed the 1st class transfer.
The Mystic class includes all wizards and healers.

Warrior Class
Warrior, Knight, Rogue, Gladiator, Paladin, Warlord, Dark Avenger, Treasure Hunter, Hawkeye, Elven Knight, Elven Scout, Temple Knight, Swordsinger, Plain Walker, Silver Ranger, Palus Knight, Assassin, Shilien Knight, Blade Dancer, Abyss Walker, Phantom Ranger, Orc Raider, Orc Monk, Destroyer, Tyrant, Scavenger, Artisan, Bounty Hunter, Warsmith, Trooper, Warder, Berserker, Soul Breaker and Arbalester.
Mystic Class
Wizard, Sorcerer, Necromancer, Warlock, Elven Wizard, Spellsinger, Elemental Summoner, Dark Wizard, Spellhowler and Phantom Summoner.
Healer Class
Cleric, Bishop, Prophet, Oracle, Elder, Shilien Oracle, Shilien Elder, Orc Shaman, Overlord, Warcryer and Inspector.
